nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE CONTINUES WEST-NORTHWESTWARD OVER THE CENTRAL EAST PACIFIC...
summary: ...HENRIETTE CONTINUES WEST-NORTHWESTWARD OVER THE CENTRAL EAST PACIFIC... As of 11:00 PM HST Mon Aug 04 the center of Henriette was located near 15.9, -123.1 with movement WNW at 15 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1003 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
